<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>We Received Your Message</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
    .header { font-size: 18px; color: #28a745; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .label { font-weight: bold; }
    .value { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">✅ Thank You, <%= data.firstName %>!</div>

    <p>We’ve received your message and will get back to you shortly.</p>

    <p><span class="label">Here's what you sent:</span></p>
    <p><span class="label">Name:</span> <%= data.firstName %> <%= data.lastName %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Email:</span> <%= data.email %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Phone:</span> <%= data.phone %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Message:</span><br><%= data.message %></p>

    <hr>
    <p>Thanks for reaching out via my portfolio site!</p>
    <p>- Manthan Makode</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>